WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
â™ªThat dayâ™ª

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
â™ªNothing stays together foreverâ™ª

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
â™ªI've quit romanceâ™ª

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
â™ªWho hasn't failed againâ™ª

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
â™ªCrying in deathâ™ª

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
â™ªAnd in lifeâ™ª

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
â™ªEven nowâ™ª

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
â™ªWe keep learningâ™ª

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
â™ªIt's no surpriseâ™ª

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
â™ªBeing happy is so hardâ™ª

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
â™ªWeirdly, I became a role modelâ™ª

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
â™ªOn the day we met again, we said hiâ™ª

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
â™ªIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintâ™ª

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
â™ªWho can do anything without regretâ™ª

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
â™ªI am all rightâ™ª

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
â™ªMay you live in peaceâ™ª

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
â™ªLet the world roarâ™ª

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
â™ªSounds like a carnivalâ™ª

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
â™ªBeing alive is never dullâ™ª

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
â™ªHow wonderful to be freeâ™ª

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
â™ªI became even better without youâ™ª

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
â™ªNothing can be perfectâ™ª

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
â™ªWe bless each other in painâ™ª

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
â™ªWe nod and smileâ™ª

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
â™ªMay we both be wellâ™ª

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:44.003
=Episode 27=

01:46.426 --> 01:47.066
Chen Lin.

01:48.306 --> 01:49.825
What do you think of me?

01:50.465 --> 01:51.265
You're kind,

01:51.946 --> 01:52.465
wise,

01:53.146 --> 01:53.666
open-minded,

01:54.026 --> 01:55.306
visionary, magnanimous,

01:55.946 --> 01:57.625
and calm in crisis.

02:00.426 --> 02:02.066
Am I Mr. Shen of Jinda Group,

02:04.506 --> 02:05.465
or Shen Haoming?

02:06.745 --> 02:07.345
Well...

02:08.345 --> 02:09.386
What's the difference?

02:15.826 --> 02:16.465
Mr. Shen,

02:17.345 --> 02:18.426
I have a suggestion.

02:19.625 --> 02:21.465
We're going to invest
in cultural tourism

02:21.505 --> 02:22.586
in Gubei Town, right?

02:23.345 --> 02:25.026
You take Haochen there every year.

02:25.945 --> 02:27.586
The environment is excellent.

02:28.225 --> 02:28.866
Give yourself

02:29.465 --> 02:30.146
some days off.

02:32.345 --> 02:33.785
I have so much work.

02:35.986 --> 02:37.465
Why not set aside

02:37.905 --> 02:39.426
the business for now?

02:40.185 --> 02:41.266
I heard they're

02:41.426 --> 02:43.465
hosting some folk festival there.

02:44.185 --> 02:45.106
There's local food,

02:45.905 --> 02:48.065
local handicrafts,
and botanical dyeing workshops.

02:48.426 --> 02:49.185
It's so lively.

02:51.505 --> 02:52.785
Take over the company affairs.

02:53.185 --> 02:54.465
I'll be on a business trip.

02:55.106 --> 02:56.065
I understand.

02:57.465 --> 02:58.986
We'll get back to you after

02:59.065 --> 02:59.706
re-evaluation.

03:00.546 --> 03:01.505
Okay, talk later.

03:03.266 --> 03:03.665
Yan.

03:03.945 --> 03:04.826
(Paid Promotion Plan)
Here is

03:04.905 --> 03:06.306
my paid promotion plan.

03:06.386 --> 03:08.106
I plan to upload six to eight

03:08.306 --> 03:10.306
original videos across platforms.

03:10.546 --> 03:12.426
(After sale)
In one to two hours after posting,

03:12.505 --> 03:13.625
if the completion rate,

03:13.706 --> 03:15.026
likes, and comments look good,

03:15.106 --> 03:16.266
we'll go for

03:16.546 --> 03:17.665
paid promotions.

03:18.065 --> 03:18.505
Alright.

03:19.426 --> 03:20.945
Do as you say. Let me see.

03:21.026 --> 03:21.625
Got it, Yan.

03:21.745 --> 03:22.586
I'm off then.

03:22.745 --> 03:23.106
Okay.

03:27.225 --> 03:27.625
Yan,

03:28.505 --> 03:29.625
take a look and sign this.

03:35.306 --> 03:35.625
Right.

03:36.185 --> 03:37.866
Mr. Zhang from Gubei Town called to ask

03:37.866 --> 03:38.785
when you're visiting.

03:42.266 --> 03:43.026
I forgot.

03:46.625 --> 03:47.745
Sorry, I was swamped.

03:48.146 --> 03:48.986
No worries.

03:49.345 --> 03:50.386
Take a break.

03:50.586 --> 03:52.065
Consider this field trip

03:52.266 --> 03:53.106
a vacation.

03:53.306 --> 03:54.546
Stop bottling things up.

03:54.706 --> 03:55.106
Okay?

03:57.306 --> 03:59.106
If everything goes smoothly

03:59.426 --> 04:00.826
with this new episode, I'll go.

04:01.345 --> 04:02.625
I'll leave the work to you.

04:03.146 --> 04:03.546
Okay.

04:04.306 --> 04:04.866
Thank you.

04:07.225 --> 04:07.745
What's wrong?

04:09.986 --> 04:10.785
Your signature.

04:12.386 --> 04:12.826
Okay.

04:12.826 --> 04:14.608
(Signed by Party B: Xu Yan)

04:15.930 --> 04:20.272
â™ªCause I just have been hurt
too many timesâ™ª

04:22.202 --> 04:26.672
â™ªI'm giving it all,
just getting nothing backâ™ª

04:28.282 --> 04:33.734
â™ªI was lost in the dark,
and it's too hurt to even seeâ™ª

04:34.714 --> 04:39.440
â™ªSee the world and how it flows.
We never let goâ™ª

04:41.345 --> 04:42.305
Ms. Xu.

04:42.785 --> 04:43.985
We've been eagerly

04:43.985 --> 04:45.345
waiting for you.

04:47.146 --> 04:47.586
Hello.

04:47.802 --> 04:52.225
â™ªThe love that I should deserveâ™ª

04:52.225 --> 04:53.386
Sorry for all the trouble,

04:54.066 --> 04:54.985
Mr. Zhang.

04:55.225 --> 04:55.865
Not at all.

04:56.506 --> 04:58.785
Welcome to Gubei Town for inspection.

04:59.706 --> 05:00.946
It's been a long journey.

05:01.665 --> 05:03.465
It's even prettier than I imagined.

05:03.865 --> 05:04.586
It gets better.

05:05.066 --> 05:06.305
Let me show you around.

05:06.665 --> 05:07.066
Alright.

05:07.186 --> 05:08.026
Your room is there.

05:08.026 --> 05:08.425
Thanks.

05:09.345 --> 05:09.665
Come on.

05:11.186 --> 05:12.386
This place is thriving.

05:12.425 --> 05:12.905
Yeah.

05:14.186 --> 05:15.345
We need experts like you

05:15.345 --> 05:16.425
to help promote us.

05:16.545 --> 05:17.785
You can count on me.

05:26.105 --> 05:27.066
Be careful.

05:27.186 --> 05:27.626
Alright.

05:31.345 --> 05:31.905
Well?

05:32.626 --> 05:33.305
To be fair,

05:33.905 --> 05:35.345
you've become a better boatman

05:35.946 --> 05:36.706
than me.

05:37.465 --> 05:38.865
I learned from the best.

05:39.425 --> 05:39.946
Thanks.

05:47.969 --> 05:49.520
(Watertown Gubei)

05:50.785 --> 05:52.545
This is stunning.

05:52.785 --> 05:54.066
It's beautiful.

05:54.586 --> 05:56.826
This place fuses the majestic northern

05:56.985 --> 05:58.066
architectural styles

05:58.186 --> 06:00.865
as well as the delicate elegance

06:00.865 --> 06:01.985
of Jiangnan water towns.

06:02.345 --> 06:03.225
There is nothing

06:03.266 --> 06:03.946
like this.

06:04.026 --> 06:04.626
So unique.

06:05.026 --> 06:06.266
Gubei Town has seen

06:06.266 --> 06:07.386
remarkable development.

06:07.506 --> 06:08.826
We've built our own canteen,

06:09.225 --> 06:09.905
tourist center,

06:10.545 --> 06:11.586
organic vegetable farms,

06:11.905 --> 06:12.746
and dyeing workshops

06:12.865 --> 06:13.865
that have improved

06:13.905 --> 06:14.746
our quality of life.

06:15.545 --> 06:17.026
That's impressive.

06:17.186 --> 06:18.785
But not many tourists know.

06:18.946 --> 06:20.386
That's why we need you

06:20.386 --> 06:21.465
to help promote

06:21.545 --> 06:22.305
our town.

06:22.465 --> 06:23.105
Rest assured.

06:23.105 --> 06:24.706
- We will certainly do our best...
- Sir?

06:25.506 --> 06:26.105
What's up?

06:27.706 --> 06:29.345
I'm showing our higher-up

06:29.545 --> 06:30.345
around the town.

06:30.425 --> 06:30.905
Hello.

06:30.905 --> 06:31.425
Hello.

06:31.506 --> 06:32.186
I'm Xu Yan.

06:33.066 --> 06:33.586
Hello.

06:34.225 --> 06:34.545
Have...

06:35.345 --> 06:36.345
Have we met before?

06:36.785 --> 06:38.105
You do look familiar.

06:38.266 --> 06:39.146
Let me introduce you.

06:39.665 --> 06:40.626
This is the owner of

06:40.785 --> 06:41.865
our town's Sky Lounge.

06:41.985 --> 06:42.706
This is Ms. Xu.

06:43.305 --> 06:43.946
Hello, Ma'am.

06:44.026 --> 06:44.746
Nice to meet you.

06:44.946 --> 06:46.386
Our Sky Lounge offers

06:46.465 --> 06:48.665
the best panoramic views in Gubei Town.

06:48.665 --> 06:48.905
Yeah.

06:49.026 --> 06:50.706
I'll give you a discount when you come.

06:51.225 --> 06:51.746
Welcome.

06:52.305 --> 06:52.905
I'm honored.

06:53.345 --> 06:53.626
Okay.

06:54.066 --> 06:54.626
See you.

06:54.746 --> 06:55.465
I'll visit.

06:55.586 --> 06:56.386
I promise, Ma'am.

06:56.826 --> 06:57.345
Okay.

06:57.545 --> 06:58.465
Hospitable, huh?

07:01.105 --> 07:01.706
Wu.

07:03.225 --> 07:03.785
Haoming.

07:03.785 --> 07:04.785
Where are you going?

07:04.905 --> 07:06.545
Won't you come to make kites today?

07:06.865 --> 07:07.386
Not today.

07:07.506 --> 07:08.865
I'll learn botanical dyeing.

07:09.586 --> 07:10.826
The kites you made last time

07:10.826 --> 07:11.586
were exceptional.

07:11.746 --> 07:12.506
They're sold out.

07:12.785 --> 07:14.146
You've mastered this skill.

07:14.146 --> 07:14.785
What do I do?

07:15.026 --> 07:16.425
Maybe, I can open

07:16.465 --> 07:17.146
a branch store.

07:17.425 --> 07:17.946
You...

07:18.186 --> 07:19.386
Just take over my shop

07:19.425 --> 07:20.345
and be the manager.

07:20.386 --> 07:20.865
No way.

07:21.706 --> 07:23.186
Remember that agave-shaped kite

07:23.186 --> 07:23.985
you asked for?

07:24.026 --> 07:24.905
Let me fetch it.

07:24.946 --> 07:25.865
Okay.

07:27.105 --> 07:28.586
When is the botanical dyeing class

07:28.626 --> 07:29.586
going to start?

07:29.785 --> 07:31.146
I've scheduled it for you.

07:31.586 --> 07:32.545
The workshop is near

07:32.586 --> 07:33.425
your accommodations.

07:33.586 --> 07:34.105
Check in.

07:34.225 --> 07:35.066
Get settled.

07:35.146 --> 07:35.826
Head there

07:35.946 --> 07:37.305
and study as long as you want.

07:37.465 --> 07:38.026
Thank you.

07:38.186 --> 07:39.280
Our Commercial Street.

07:39.425 --> 07:39.746
Okay.

07:39.905 --> 07:40.905
Go ahead.

07:40.946 --> 07:42.266
I've got kites to finish here.

07:42.345 --> 07:42.665
Okay.

07:42.746 --> 07:43.600
- Ride safely.
- Bye.

07:43.746 --> 07:44.266
This shop

07:44.586 --> 07:45.946
sells unique kites.

07:46.225 --> 07:47.386
They fly high and far.

07:47.545 --> 07:48.186
You think

07:48.386 --> 07:48.985
it's gone.

07:49.105 --> 07:49.706
Pull the string

07:49.905 --> 07:50.506
and it's back.

07:50.746 --> 07:51.425
People wonder,

07:51.626 --> 07:52.465
"Is it gone?"

07:52.826 --> 07:54.865
But they can always pull it back.

07:55.225 --> 07:56.706
Everyone loves their kites.

07:59.665 --> 08:00.626
Ms... Ms. Xu.

08:00.865 --> 08:01.506
Ms. Xu.

08:03.266 --> 08:03.785
What's wrong?

08:05.305 --> 08:05.746
Nothing.

08:06.266 --> 08:07.345
Let's keep going.

08:10.066 --> 08:11.266
This is

08:11.266 --> 08:12.545
our best guesthouse.

08:13.225 --> 08:14.626
The room you're staying in

08:15.506 --> 08:16.586
is the finest room

08:16.626 --> 08:18.066
specifically

08:18.186 --> 08:19.706
reserved for you

08:19.905 --> 08:20.946
by our director.

08:21.105 --> 08:21.826
Thank you, Hua.

08:22.186 --> 08:22.746
Thank you.

08:22.946 --> 08:23.506
No problem.

08:24.946 --> 08:25.386
Right.

08:25.545 --> 08:26.345
Our town

08:26.345 --> 08:27.826
isn't exactly small.

08:28.186 --> 08:29.746
We've prepared an electric scooter

08:30.105 --> 08:31.425
for you to roam around.

08:32.506 --> 08:33.065
Ms. Xu.

08:34.905 --> 08:35.346
Ms. Xu.

08:36.785 --> 08:37.346
Can you ride?

08:37.585 --> 08:38.106
Yeah.

08:38.905 --> 08:39.506
I thought you

08:39.545 --> 08:40.266
couldn't ride it.

08:40.506 --> 08:40.746
Well,

08:40.785 --> 08:41.506
rest well.

08:41.905 --> 08:42.506
Call me

08:42.506 --> 08:42.986
later.

08:43.146 --> 08:44.746
I'll show you the itinerary.

08:45.346 --> 08:46.545
Thank you, Sir.

08:46.825 --> 08:47.386
Thank you.

08:48.346 --> 08:49.065
Get some rest.

08:49.425 --> 08:50.000
- Okay.
- Okay.

08:51.305 --> 08:51.705
Bye.

08:51.705 --> 08:52.146
Take care.

09:01.266 --> 09:01.785
Doesn't beep.

09:09.306 --> 09:10.832
â™ªIt's no surpriseâ™ª

09:10.832 --> 09:11.696
â™ªHard to be happyâ™ª

09:11.696 --> 09:15.024
â™ªI only hope that one dayâ™ª

09:15.354 --> 09:17.392
â™ªWhat's mine will comeâ™ª

09:17.392 --> 09:23.504
â™ªEmerging from the crowd for meâ™ª

09:23.504 --> 09:26.333
â™ªThen regrets won't lingerâ™ª

09:26.522 --> 09:30.662
â™ªI am all rightâ™ª

09:30.970 --> 09:35.760
â™ªMay you live in peaceâ™ª

09:35.760 --> 09:38.192
â™ªLet the world roarâ™ª

09:38.192 --> 09:40.432
â™ªSounds like a carnivalâ™ª

09:40.432 --> 09:44.944
â™ªBeing alive is never dullâ™ª

09:47.066 --> 09:48.496
â™ªOvercomeâ™ª

09:48.496 --> 09:51.500
â™ªThe obstacles and love ourselvesâ™ª

09:51.962 --> 09:55.760
â™ªBe so good that you can't recognize meâ™ª

09:55.898 --> 09:58.256
â™ªWhen I can look upâ™ª

09:58.256 --> 10:01.264
(Yongshun Botanical Dyeing)
â™ªAt different cloudsâ™ª

10:01.264 --> 10:02.986
â™ªI'll embrace the memoriesâ™ª

10:02.986 --> 10:04.106
Throughout the history,

10:04.146 --> 10:05.665
our ancestors developed

10:06.106 --> 10:07.026
vast insights

10:07.065 --> 10:08.146
into colors

10:08.945 --> 10:09.866
and discovered methods

10:09.945 --> 10:10.785
to extract pigments

10:10.905 --> 10:12.185
from nature.

10:13.386 --> 10:14.545
Botanical dyeing

10:14.785 --> 10:17.626
utilizes natural plants
to color textiles,

10:18.026 --> 10:19.506
which is a technique deriving from

10:20.106 --> 10:21.065
and returning

10:21.425 --> 10:22.185
to nature.

10:23.280 --> 10:24.986
"The Exploitation
of the Works of Nature"

10:24.986 --> 10:26.425
recorded over twenty methods

10:26.506 --> 10:28.065
of plant-based dyeing.

10:28.746 --> 10:29.945
In modern terms,

10:30.106 --> 10:30.746
they're natural

10:31.026 --> 10:31.545
and

10:31.905 --> 10:32.496
eco-friendly.

10:34.305 --> 10:35.146
Take a look.

10:35.986 --> 10:38.665
Blue, red, yellow, white, and black.

10:39.386 --> 10:40.266
These are

10:40.386 --> 10:40.986
primary colors.

10:41.585 --> 10:42.386
Mixing primaries

10:42.466 --> 10:43.705
yields secondary hues,

10:44.146 --> 10:45.266
while mordant treatments,

10:45.346 --> 10:46.106
color blending,

10:46.185 --> 10:47.905
and overdyeing techniques...

10:47.905 --> 10:48.665
Excuse me.

10:48.665 --> 10:49.305
I'm late.

10:49.305 --> 10:49.866
It's okay.

10:50.905 --> 10:51.825
These methods

10:52.185 --> 10:54.185
yield infinite color variations.

10:55.466 --> 10:56.226
Furthermore,

10:56.466 --> 10:57.986
botanical dyeing accommodates

10:58.065 --> 10:59.026
various fabric types.

10:59.386 --> 11:01.305
Silk, cotton, and linen all work.

11:02.106 --> 11:02.866
Do you know

11:03.305 --> 11:04.866
which plants produce

11:05.346 --> 11:06.585
these different colors?

11:08.305 --> 11:09.545
Botanical dyeing transforms

11:09.545 --> 11:10.825
nature's palette

11:10.905 --> 11:12.026
onto textiles.

11:12.466 --> 11:14.065
For greens,

11:14.386 --> 11:16.986
you can use fresh leaves,

11:17.346 --> 11:19.026
sophora buds,

11:20.705 --> 11:21.346
or dye flowers.

11:21.986 --> 11:23.226
Yellow hues

11:23.346 --> 11:24.905
come from turmeric,

11:25.506 --> 11:26.065
mugwort,

11:26.305 --> 11:27.065
or gardenia.

11:27.506 --> 11:29.065
Even common foods and fruits

11:29.466 --> 11:31.106
like blueberries,

11:31.425 --> 11:32.705
bayberries,

11:33.226 --> 11:34.185
and red cabbage

11:34.185 --> 11:35.425
can serve as dyes.

11:36.266 --> 11:37.425
Well done, Shen.

11:37.665 --> 11:39.226
Your extra classes show.

11:41.106 --> 11:41.905
Today,

11:42.185 --> 11:43.266
we'll practice

11:43.386 --> 11:44.746
basic dyeing techniques.

11:45.386 --> 11:46.065
Follow me.

12:00.425 --> 12:01.425
There are some

12:01.585 --> 12:02.506
plain pottery blanks.

12:03.106 --> 12:04.305
Choose one and dye it

12:04.305 --> 12:05.825
with the colors you like.

12:06.226 --> 12:07.545
Very few people know

12:08.106 --> 12:09.146
that our traditional

12:09.146 --> 12:10.425
24 solar terms

12:10.585 --> 12:12.026
have corresponding colors.

12:13.226 --> 12:15.346
The Minor Snow solar term in winter

12:15.866 --> 12:17.466
starts with crimson-purple and evolves

12:17.825 --> 12:18.866
into pale purple

12:19.466 --> 12:22.746
then transforms into rouge purple.

12:23.785 --> 12:24.626
Ms. Qiuzi.

12:25.945 --> 12:26.825
I read a book

12:26.825 --> 12:29.226
from the Eastern Jin Dynasty
back in college.

12:29.305 --> 12:30.266
It recorded,

12:30.665 --> 12:31.905
"Upon the Cloud-Reaching"

12:31.945 --> 12:33.266
"Terrace,"

12:33.986 --> 12:34.945
"the king's lamps"

12:35.185 --> 12:36.026
"shone for miles,"

12:37.065 --> 12:38.026
"and their smoke"

12:38.785 --> 12:40.065
"was crimson-purple."

12:40.545 --> 12:41.825
I've always wanted to know

12:41.825 --> 12:43.026
what kind of purple it is.

12:43.785 --> 12:44.266
So,

12:44.785 --> 12:45.866
may I choose purple?

12:46.746 --> 12:48.185
You're talking about

12:48.466 --> 12:50.425
"Record of Heretofore Lost Works"
by Wang Jia,

12:50.705 --> 12:51.986
the earliest documentation

12:52.146 --> 12:53.425
of crape myrtle cultivation.

12:54.305 --> 12:54.705
Alright.

12:55.266 --> 12:56.346
Today, let's try

12:56.466 --> 12:57.785
to dye fabric

12:57.905 --> 12:58.986
crimson-purple.

12:59.785 --> 13:00.986
Due to limited space,

13:01.146 --> 13:01.785
we'll work

13:01.825 --> 13:02.746
in pairs.

13:02.905 --> 13:03.785
Please pair up.

13:04.425 --> 13:05.266
We'll team up.

13:05.386 --> 13:05.712
Okay.

13:18.146 --> 13:18.665
Thank you.

13:33.274 --> 13:35.711
â™ªSeparatedâ™ª

13:37.754 --> 13:40.863
â™ªLike the world shook off its dustâ™ª

13:44.858 --> 13:47.782
â™ªYour toughness, your innocenceâ™ª

13:47.782 --> 13:50.599
â™ªHow can I lean on you? Yet not let goâ™ª

13:50.599 --> 13:53.365
â™ªMy life was fine without youâ™ª

13:53.454 --> 13:56.400
â™ªI was happy with or without youâ™ª

13:56.400 --> 13:59.184
â™ªWhy am I missing a piece of soulâ™ª

13:59.184 --> 14:01.328
â™ªSome stubborn fools just lose all hopeâ™ª

14:01.328 --> 14:03.662
â™ªThat momentâ™ª

14:03.898 --> 14:06.389
â™ªI knew loveâ™ª

14:06.640 --> 14:08.848
â™ªYou're my oneâ™ª

14:08.848 --> 14:11.600
â™ªI realize when I lose youâ™ª

14:11.600 --> 14:14.512
â™ªThe more I let goâ™ª

14:14.512 --> 14:17.904
â™ªThe more it hurtsâ™ª

14:18.106 --> 14:20.269
â™ªI was the oneâ™ª

14:20.269 --> 14:23.120
â™ªWho chose to walk awayâ™ª

14:23.120 --> 14:25.973
â™ªIf given another chanceâ™ª

14:25.973 --> 14:29.089
â™ªLife's unwritten spaceâ™ª

14:29.089 --> 14:32.560
â™ªNow I anticipateâ™ª

14:41.882 --> 14:44.880
â™ªYour toughness, your innocenceâ™ª

14:44.880 --> 14:47.711
â™ªHow can I lean on you? Yet not let goâ™ª

14:47.711 --> 14:50.448
â™ªMy life was fine without youâ™ª

14:50.448 --> 14:53.584
â™ªI was happy with or without youâ™ª

14:53.584 --> 14:56.272
â™ªWhy am I missing a piece of soulâ™ª

14:57.146 --> 14:57.665
Be careful.

14:57.872 --> 14:58.466
Let me do it.

14:58.466 --> 15:00.656
â™ªThat momentâ™ª

15:01.018 --> 15:03.466
â™ªI knew loveâ™ª

15:03.466 --> 15:04.146
You can

15:04.466 --> 15:05.945
gently knead the fabric.

15:05.945 --> 15:08.425
â™ªI realize when I lose youâ™ª

15:08.425 --> 15:09.346
Apply enough pressure

15:10.026 --> 15:11.746
to ensure even dyeing.

15:11.746 --> 15:15.216
â™ªThe more it hurtsâ™ª

15:15.216 --> 15:17.360
â™ªI was the oneâ™ª

15:18.746 --> 15:19.746
Today we're using

15:20.065 --> 15:21.626
sappanwood for coloring.

15:21.905 --> 15:23.825
Sappanwood has strong dyeing power.

15:24.305 --> 15:26.545
But its natural color is red.

15:26.945 --> 15:28.785
To achieve purple hues,

15:29.705 --> 15:31.785
we add alkaline for color fixation.

15:32.026 --> 15:32.665
This way,

15:32.866 --> 15:33.746
we can produce

15:33.866 --> 15:35.106
the unique

15:35.466 --> 15:38.185
crimson-purple we envision.

15:41.106 --> 15:41.905
Leave the rest

15:42.386 --> 15:43.506
to time.

15:44.746 --> 15:46.905
Whether we succeed
in producing the color

15:48.026 --> 15:49.785
remains uncertain.

17:22.145 --> 17:22.906
What a surprise.

17:23.666 --> 17:24.305
You did

17:24.345 --> 17:26.305
a perfect purple dye on the first day.

17:27.666 --> 17:28.266
Tomorrow,

17:28.426 --> 17:29.746
let's experiment with blue.

17:30.145 --> 17:30.706
Okay.

17:58.426 --> 17:59.266
Shen Haoming.

18:02.666 --> 18:04.016
Don't tell me it's a coincidence.

18:05.825 --> 18:06.706
But it is.

18:07.585 --> 18:08.105
What now?

18:10.825 --> 18:11.906
Mr. Baraikin is here?

18:12.785 --> 18:13.666
I've told you

18:14.625 --> 18:16.226
to be open and honest.

18:16.426 --> 18:17.625
Don't hide anything

18:17.986 --> 18:19.545
or beat around the bush.

18:19.706 --> 18:20.706
You're busy being

18:21.825 --> 18:22.625
my neighbor

18:22.785 --> 18:23.585
and classmate.

18:24.305 --> 18:24.986
What do you want?

18:25.946 --> 18:28.105
I've been here for days.

18:30.065 --> 18:30.746
I don't buy it.

18:32.145 --> 18:33.305
I'm not justifying myself.

18:33.666 --> 18:34.145
But

18:34.506 --> 18:36.105
I have no idea you're here.

18:36.105 --> 18:36.545
Alright?

18:38.426 --> 18:38.946
Whatever.

18:39.226 --> 18:39.746
I don't care.

18:41.466 --> 18:42.785
If it bothers you, I'll leave.

18:50.506 --> 18:51.865
Just stay out of my sight.

19:18.226 --> 19:19.145
Hello? What's up?

19:19.986 --> 19:20.986
You've settled in?

19:21.186 --> 19:21.906
How is it?

19:22.865 --> 19:23.426
It's nice.

19:23.825 --> 19:24.785
Beautiful place.

19:25.506 --> 19:26.768
Shen Haoming lives next door.

19:27.266 --> 19:29.065
What's going on?

19:30.906 --> 19:32.065
He followed you there?

19:32.625 --> 19:33.946
And he lives next door?

19:35.026 --> 19:35.888
How should I know?

19:36.345 --> 19:37.746
What else could he want?

19:37.785 --> 19:38.426
It's so obvious.

19:38.506 --> 19:39.906
He went there for you.

19:40.666 --> 19:41.666
My goodness.

19:42.145 --> 19:43.666
He's so persistent.

19:45.226 --> 19:46.026
But he's only

19:46.065 --> 19:47.186
perceived as persistent

19:47.186 --> 19:48.585
if he doesn't bother

19:48.906 --> 19:49.706
anyone.

19:50.105 --> 19:51.625
But if you find him annoying,

19:51.785 --> 19:52.506
then he's just

19:52.865 --> 19:54.785
clingy and shameless.

19:55.105 --> 19:55.466
Come on.

19:55.986 --> 19:57.625
It's not that bad.

19:59.266 --> 19:59.986
Feeling sorry?

20:00.906 --> 20:02.666
You can't admit you still care?

20:03.865 --> 20:05.026
Aren't you my sister?

20:05.506 --> 20:06.865
Did you forget his scheme?

20:07.825 --> 20:09.145
I'm your sister and that's why

20:09.145 --> 20:10.426
I need to be fair.

20:10.706 --> 20:11.585
Forget about

20:11.585 --> 20:12.865
his scheme.

20:13.466 --> 20:14.865
He helped Yan Studio,

20:15.545 --> 20:16.865
which also benefits himself.

20:17.026 --> 20:18.865
As CEO of a listed company,

20:19.105 --> 20:20.666
he has a vision, doesn't he?

20:20.825 --> 20:21.986
If he were truly lovesick,

20:21.986 --> 20:22.746
could you stand it?

20:23.305 --> 20:25.426
But he always approaches me

20:25.825 --> 20:27.305
with ulterior motives.

20:29.506 --> 20:30.585
Now, I can't tell

20:30.625 --> 20:32.266
what he wants.

20:33.545 --> 20:35.266
You just won't face your feelings.

20:36.145 --> 20:37.105
Are you still into him?

20:39.746 --> 20:40.186
You won't

20:40.345 --> 20:40.666
answer?

20:40.666 --> 20:42.625
Silence means confirmation.

20:43.746 --> 20:44.105
Yan,

20:44.145 --> 20:46.105
he's not that bad.

20:46.426 --> 20:47.825
You've rejected him so many times,

20:48.026 --> 20:49.026
but he persists.

20:49.385 --> 20:50.145
He'd get anyone

20:50.145 --> 20:51.426
he's trying to pursue.

20:54.305 --> 20:55.746
He doesn't pursue anyone.

20:56.625 --> 20:57.706
That's it. I have to go.

21:05.585 --> 21:06.385
Still working?

21:07.906 --> 21:08.986
I still have

21:08.986 --> 21:09.746
some work to do.

21:10.426 --> 21:12.186
You're working too hard.

21:12.666 --> 21:14.186
You should've gone with Xu Yan.

21:14.506 --> 21:15.545
Enjoy the nice scenery

21:15.906 --> 21:16.825
and take a break.

21:17.506 --> 21:18.865
Get makeup inspirations.

21:19.785 --> 21:21.746
Someone needs to look after the company.

21:23.825 --> 21:24.880
Why are you still here?

21:26.385 --> 21:27.105
Well,

21:27.345 --> 21:29.625
we need to pay a supplier soon.

21:30.345 --> 21:31.426
I checked the accounts

21:31.946 --> 21:33.506
and our cash flow

21:33.746 --> 21:34.506
is insufficient.

21:35.466 --> 21:36.186
Short by how much?

21:36.746 --> 21:37.305
A million.

21:38.105 --> 21:38.946
A million?

21:43.226 --> 21:44.785
We increased factory orders

21:44.865 --> 21:45.986
for urgent production,

21:46.426 --> 21:47.746
so we diverted funds

21:47.906 --> 21:49.186
to advance payment

21:49.186 --> 21:50.785
for the factory.

21:53.345 --> 21:54.706
Okay. I'll handle this.

21:55.585 --> 21:57.226
You're managing everything alone.

21:57.305 --> 21:58.186
Take a break.

21:58.706 --> 21:59.466
Let me get you

21:59.825 --> 22:00.545
some dinner.

22:00.585 --> 22:01.466
No need.

22:01.706 --> 22:02.585
Braised pork rice.

22:02.666 --> 22:03.986
No need, Lin Tao.

22:05.105 --> 22:05.666
Dr. Yu.

22:08.746 --> 22:09.466
Why did you come?

22:10.305 --> 22:10.986
I'm free today,

22:11.186 --> 22:11.865
so I thought

22:12.026 --> 22:12.466
I'd come.

22:13.585 --> 22:14.746
Work can wait.

22:15.186 --> 22:16.105
Now that Dr. Yu's here,

22:16.506 --> 22:17.746
go have dinner.

22:18.065 --> 22:19.026
Rest early.

22:19.865 --> 22:20.466
Well...

22:20.666 --> 22:21.986
Guess I'm done for today.

22:22.226 --> 22:22.746
Wait for me.

22:25.105 --> 22:25.545
We're off.

22:27.065 --> 22:28.105
Turn off my PC, please.

22:28.145 --> 22:28.506
Thanks.

22:28.545 --> 22:29.026
Okay.

22:30.506 --> 22:31.345
What are we having?

22:31.946 --> 22:33.026
Hot pot?

22:33.266 --> 22:33.746
Okay.

22:50.065 --> 22:51.906
Bring my makeup bag.

22:53.946 --> 22:54.946
Did you hear me?

22:56.785 --> 22:57.625
Yeah.

22:57.986 --> 22:59.105
Where'd you put it, honey?

22:59.506 --> 23:00.466
In the suitcase.

23:00.506 --> 23:01.746
Look properly.

23:02.226 --> 23:03.186
Okay, let me check.

23:09.385 --> 23:09.986
Ms. Xu.

23:10.105 --> 23:10.946
Would you like

23:10.946 --> 23:11.785
housekeeping service?

23:12.986 --> 23:13.785
Yes, thank you.

23:14.466 --> 23:15.585
Excuse me.

23:16.385 --> 23:17.906
Where is the guest who stayed here?

23:18.065 --> 23:18.986
He has checked out.

23:28.986 --> 23:29.746
He really left?

23:34.672 --> 23:36.026
(Yongshun Botanical Dyeing)
These items

23:36.026 --> 23:37.105
displayed here

23:37.305 --> 23:38.825
are the raw materials for dyeing.

23:39.785 --> 23:41.545
These materials

23:41.785 --> 23:43.226
may look ordinary.

23:43.825 --> 23:44.506
But in reality,

23:44.706 --> 23:45.506
each of them

23:45.666 --> 23:47.825
has hidden properties
you wouldn't expect.

23:50.625 --> 23:51.426
Xu Yan?

23:52.186 --> 23:52.986
Ms. Qiuzi.

23:54.105 --> 23:55.746
Do you know what this is?

23:57.906 --> 23:58.426
Sorry.

23:58.426 --> 23:59.585
I have no idea.

24:00.266 --> 24:02.145
This is called Chinese Indigo.

24:02.785 --> 24:04.545
The common indigo blue we see

24:04.865 --> 24:06.666
is extracted from this plant.

24:07.105 --> 24:07.746
Blue?

24:08.825 --> 24:10.226
This can produce blue dye?

24:10.506 --> 24:11.065
Yeah.

24:11.585 --> 24:12.305
Take a look.

24:12.345 --> 24:13.385
These indigo leaves

24:13.426 --> 24:14.666
need several days of soaking

24:14.865 --> 24:15.986
to release their pigments.

24:16.426 --> 24:17.585
Then we add lime,

24:17.666 --> 24:18.865
ferment it, and let it settle

24:19.345 --> 24:21.065
to get the indigo paste.

24:22.305 --> 24:23.065
So today,

24:23.506 --> 24:25.105
we'll try using this indigo paste

24:25.426 --> 24:26.186
to dye blue.

24:26.666 --> 24:27.186
Follow me.

24:39.585 --> 24:40.266
Hello, sir.

24:40.466 --> 24:41.305
Feel free to browse.

24:44.625 --> 24:46.385
These are all handmade.

24:46.585 --> 24:47.785
Do you like it?

24:48.026 --> 24:48.825
Look around.

24:49.785 --> 24:50.266
It's pretty.

24:50.506 --> 24:51.065
Handmade.

24:51.625 --> 24:52.026
Okay.

24:52.625 --> 24:54.145
I wanted to ask

24:55.305 --> 24:56.186
if you have

24:57.426 --> 24:59.466
an agave-shaped kite?

24:59.706 --> 25:01.226
That's customized.

25:01.466 --> 25:02.946
Do you know the person

25:02.946 --> 25:04.266
who ordered an agave kite?

25:04.585 --> 25:05.666
Haoming.

25:08.026 --> 25:09.266
Shen Haoming from Jinda Group.

25:09.305 --> 25:09.706
Right?

25:10.385 --> 25:11.906
We're old acquaintances.

25:11.906 --> 25:13.625
On your way here,

25:13.706 --> 25:14.305
did you notice

25:14.345 --> 25:16.625
the tourist center, the vegetable farm,

25:16.625 --> 25:17.426
and our canteen?

25:17.585 --> 25:18.986
Jinda Group built those.

25:19.186 --> 25:20.625
It's been years.

25:25.305 --> 25:26.906
So he wasn't pretending?

25:27.466 --> 25:28.026
He was.

25:30.506 --> 25:31.105
He was?

25:31.506 --> 25:32.385
To be a tourist.

25:32.906 --> 25:33.746
At first,

25:33.746 --> 25:35.305
we thought he was just a tourist.

25:35.585 --> 25:36.746
But then, the townspeople

25:37.186 --> 25:38.345
said he's from Jinda Group.

25:38.466 --> 25:39.226
Interesting guy.

25:39.385 --> 25:40.986
He came here and said,

25:41.266 --> 25:42.666
"These are handmade, right?"

25:42.706 --> 25:43.466
"Teach me."

25:43.666 --> 25:45.785
Skyscraper builders
are different, I tell you.

25:45.986 --> 25:46.585
Fast learner.

25:47.305 --> 25:48.105
The kites he made

25:48.385 --> 25:48.946
all got sold.

25:49.145 --> 25:50.385
He stole all my techniques.

25:50.706 --> 25:51.986
There's nothing else to learn.

25:52.345 --> 25:52.785
And then

25:52.986 --> 25:54.065
he went to steal

25:54.105 --> 25:55.145
techniques of

25:55.385 --> 25:56.065
botanical dyeing.

25:56.105 --> 25:56.625
You know?

26:00.305 --> 26:01.706
Do you know him?

26:01.865 --> 26:02.746
Are you his friend?

26:03.466 --> 26:04.026
A classmate.

26:05.785 --> 26:07.105
Pick a kite

26:07.105 --> 26:08.105
you like.

26:08.466 --> 26:09.026
I like it.

26:10.706 --> 26:11.466
I'll take this one.

26:12.305 --> 26:14.946
But I want to customize

26:16.466 --> 26:17.266
an agave one.

26:19.426 --> 26:19.946
Mr. Shen.

26:20.785 --> 26:22.065
I just don't get it.

26:22.906 --> 26:24.065
Did you come to Gubei Town

26:24.506 --> 26:25.746
for Xu Yan

26:26.145 --> 26:27.226
or botanical dyeing?

26:37.746 --> 26:38.545
She said she wanted

26:39.545 --> 26:41.186
to create a botanical dyeing series.

26:42.785 --> 26:44.345
That's why I came

26:45.305 --> 26:47.105
to study this technique for her.

26:48.625 --> 26:50.305
She's still mad at me because of

26:50.345 --> 26:51.226
Mr. Baraikin.

26:54.145 --> 26:54.906
I can only

26:55.545 --> 26:56.986
secretly support her.

26:57.785 --> 26:59.026
Love the tree, love the branch.

26:59.625 --> 27:00.145
But

27:00.545 --> 27:02.026
since we've run into Yan here,

27:02.506 --> 27:03.585
it's destiny at work.

27:04.625 --> 27:06.625
Why did you move out of the guesthouse

27:07.266 --> 27:08.145
to avoid her?

27:09.105 --> 27:10.345
You think I wanted to?

27:10.865 --> 27:11.906
I wouldn't believe

27:12.385 --> 27:14.145
such a coincidence either, okay?

27:15.666 --> 27:16.865
She must think

27:16.865 --> 27:17.746
I'm someone

27:18.266 --> 27:19.026
scheming

27:19.506 --> 27:20.266
and clingy.

27:21.466 --> 27:22.186
She even told me

27:23.666 --> 27:25.266
not to show up again.

27:26.746 --> 27:27.946
I don't want to upset her,

27:28.305 --> 27:29.186
so I'm staying away.

27:31.625 --> 27:33.186
A man like you

27:33.706 --> 27:34.986
is truly our role model.

27:35.585 --> 27:36.585
I have so much to learn.

27:38.426 --> 27:39.266
I almost forgot

27:39.746 --> 27:40.666
about the theater play

27:41.026 --> 27:41.785
rehearsal.

27:42.785 --> 27:43.266
Rehearsal?

27:44.426 --> 27:46.065
At least grab a bite first.

27:46.128 --> 27:46.736
(Execution of Chen Shimei)

27:48.385 --> 27:50.746
Casting for The Execution of Chen Shimei

27:51.026 --> 27:52.345
begins now.

27:52.625 --> 27:53.466
Bravo!

28:00.426 --> 28:02.986
Wu!

28:13.145 --> 28:14.426
The guesthouse owner said

28:14.466 --> 28:16.706
there's a play rehearsal
at the theater tonight.

28:17.986 --> 28:18.706
Which play?

28:19.065 --> 28:20.545
Something about Chen Shimei.

28:20.785 --> 28:22.105
She's playing the princess.

28:22.785 --> 28:23.385
Really?

28:23.585 --> 28:24.186
Let's see.

28:24.785 --> 28:26.226
Don't you dare become Chen Shimei.

28:26.785 --> 28:27.345
Never.

28:27.706 --> 28:29.666
I'll always support you.

28:30.226 --> 28:31.226
Such a sweet talker.

28:44.585 --> 28:46.145
Chen Shimei.

28:46.825 --> 28:49.585
Do you recognize your wife,

28:49.865 --> 28:51.266
Qin Xianglian?

28:52.625 --> 28:53.466
Your Honor.

28:54.426 --> 28:56.186
I'm Chen Shimei's

28:56.266 --> 28:57.906
one true wife.

28:58.585 --> 29:01.305
If Qin Xianglian drops the lawsuit,

29:01.706 --> 29:05.305
I'll give her 500 taels of silver.

29:05.545 --> 29:07.345
You abused your power

29:08.345 --> 29:09.466
and showed no remorse.

29:10.105 --> 29:11.345
This is outrageous.

29:11.746 --> 29:12.305
Guards.

29:13.426 --> 29:14.226
Execute him.

29:14.545 --> 29:15.385
Understood.

29:18.585 --> 29:19.825
Judge Bao, show mercy.

29:20.226 --> 29:21.785
Don't kill my husband.

29:21.946 --> 29:22.706
No.

29:24.105 --> 29:25.105
Your Honor.

29:26.105 --> 29:26.706
Execute him.

29:27.865 --> 29:28.466
Wait.

29:29.746 --> 29:30.906
I mean,

29:31.105 --> 29:32.305
can we revise the script?

29:33.466 --> 29:34.065
What?

29:34.145 --> 29:34.825
Go ahead.

29:35.466 --> 29:36.746
It's a modern adaptation.

29:37.105 --> 29:38.145
Shouldn't it reflect

29:38.145 --> 29:39.305
contemporary values?

29:40.266 --> 29:41.585
In today's context,

29:41.625 --> 29:42.865
the protagonist

29:43.305 --> 29:44.666
shouldn't be Chen Shimei.

29:44.906 --> 29:45.986
You mean...?

29:46.545 --> 29:47.825
Focus on the ladies.

29:48.226 --> 29:48.906
Think about it.

29:49.226 --> 29:51.305
Chen Shimei is an ungrateful

29:51.785 --> 29:52.906
social climber.

29:53.305 --> 29:55.105
Why would two women fight over him?

29:55.426 --> 29:55.906
Yeah.

29:56.666 --> 29:57.906
Brilliant insight.

29:58.706 --> 29:59.865
Mr. Shen, this is genius.

30:01.065 --> 30:02.666
He really loves acting.

30:03.345 --> 30:04.266
I get your point.

30:04.266 --> 30:04.625
Listen.

30:04.825 --> 30:05.785
See if I'm right.

30:06.506 --> 30:07.585
Qin chased her husband

30:07.946 --> 30:08.746
for a millennium

30:08.906 --> 30:10.506
and arrived at our Gubei Town.

30:10.946 --> 30:12.226
This is destiny.

30:12.746 --> 30:13.865
For such a destiny,

30:14.105 --> 30:15.545
shouldn't we let Qin Xianglian

30:15.706 --> 30:16.385
enjoy her life

30:16.785 --> 30:17.625
and have some fun?

30:18.785 --> 30:19.426
Make the guy

30:19.706 --> 30:20.466
pursue her.

30:20.825 --> 30:23.666
Let Chen Shimei pursue his wife.

30:24.666 --> 30:25.506
Something like that.

30:25.706 --> 30:27.226
No wonder I couldn't get immersed.

30:27.385 --> 30:28.385
Yeah, let's do this.

30:28.746 --> 30:29.305
Pursue her?

30:29.706 --> 30:30.426
Genius.

30:31.785 --> 30:33.506
That's what I want to see.

30:33.906 --> 30:36.186
Yeah, good point.

30:36.385 --> 30:37.065
Excellent.

30:37.065 --> 30:37.706
Make up

30:37.785 --> 30:38.706
some lines then.

30:39.026 --> 30:39.426
Right?

30:39.426 --> 30:40.545
We'll follow your lead.

30:41.186 --> 30:41.706
Great idea.

30:42.865 --> 30:43.706
Something came up.

30:45.186 --> 30:45.666
Mr. Shen.

30:46.065 --> 30:46.865
- Come back.
- Where are you going?

30:47.026 --> 30:48.145
But this is

30:48.345 --> 30:48.865
your idea.

30:48.906 --> 30:49.825
Where are you going?

30:50.466 --> 30:50.946
Come back.

30:50.946 --> 30:51.466
Mr. Shen.

30:52.545 --> 30:53.906
Don't go. It's your idea.

30:54.266 --> 30:54.865
Go on.

30:55.065 --> 30:56.545
I don't know how to change

30:56.585 --> 30:57.305
the script.

30:57.305 --> 30:58.105
Chen Shimei.

30:59.585 --> 31:00.625
Why are you shunning me?

31:01.946 --> 31:02.385
I'm not.

31:04.825 --> 31:05.585
Am I scary?

31:06.946 --> 31:07.506
I'm tired.

31:08.186 --> 31:08.946
Tired or guilty?

31:10.946 --> 31:11.946
You said you didn't

31:12.266 --> 31:13.746
want to see me, so I'm trying

31:14.506 --> 31:15.426
not to upset you.

31:15.506 --> 31:16.906
Why don't you leave?

31:18.666 --> 31:19.746
I came

31:20.065 --> 31:21.385
to learn botanical dyeing.

31:22.785 --> 31:24.145
What for?

31:26.785 --> 31:28.706
I want to share some common topics

31:29.466 --> 31:30.946
with you one day.

31:32.058 --> 31:36.026
â™ªI just wanna take my time tonightâ™ª

31:36.026 --> 31:37.426
What are you plotting now?

31:39.105 --> 31:40.186
I mean it.

31:40.625 --> 31:41.666
You said you want to learn

31:41.666 --> 31:42.585
botanical dyeing.

31:43.545 --> 31:44.506
So I wanted

31:44.986 --> 31:45.865
to study it first.

31:46.746 --> 31:48.706
Maybe it becomes our common interest.

31:52.226 --> 31:52.706
Besides,

31:52.746 --> 31:54.345
regarding the question you asked,

31:55.385 --> 31:57.266
I want to find the answers here.

31:57.498 --> 32:01.426
â™ªCause I just have been hurt
too many timesâ™ª

32:01.426 --> 32:03.226
Please don't get me wrong.

32:03.994 --> 32:08.269
â™ªI'm giving it all,
just getting nothing backâ™ª

32:10.105 --> 32:10.986
Suit yourself.

32:13.625 --> 32:14.625
Stop shunning me.

32:17.026 --> 32:18.666
Can I still be your classmate?

32:19.825 --> 32:20.906
Just don't be late.

32:22.746 --> 32:25.899
â™ªSo I'll take my timeâ™ª

32:26.138 --> 32:29.301
â™ªTo reigniteâ™ª

32:29.434 --> 32:33.840
â™ªThe love that I should deserveâ™ª

32:36.105 --> 32:38.906
You and I fly together forever.

32:39.385 --> 32:40.266
People in our town

32:40.466 --> 32:42.585
have practiced ancient dyeing techniques

32:42.906 --> 32:44.746
for over a century.

32:45.385 --> 32:46.426
The exhibits here

32:46.666 --> 32:47.746
showcase works

32:47.986 --> 32:49.906
by our master artisans.

32:51.145 --> 32:52.746
You've learned the theory

32:52.785 --> 32:53.865
and basic practice.

32:54.625 --> 32:55.226
Here,

32:55.426 --> 32:57.226
you'll feel the charm

32:57.545 --> 32:58.706
of botanical dyeing.

32:59.585 --> 33:00.065
Look.

33:00.545 --> 33:01.946
(Zhaxie)
This is Zhaxie,

33:02.585 --> 33:04.105
commonly called tie-dye.

33:05.186 --> 33:06.706
Botanical dyeing

33:07.186 --> 33:09.145
is a fusion of nature and time.

33:10.065 --> 33:10.785
It's calming

33:11.506 --> 33:12.186
and soothing.

33:14.785 --> 33:17.026
Ahead is Jiaxie.

33:18.426 --> 33:19.065
Jiexie.

33:19.065 --> 33:20.528
(Jiaxie)

33:21.305 --> 33:21.825
This

33:22.666 --> 33:23.906
carries a rustic vibe.

33:24.706 --> 33:25.906
The blue hue is powerful.

33:27.105 --> 33:29.226
(Laxie)
Over here is Laxie,

33:29.785 --> 33:31.145
also known as

33:31.585 --> 33:32.785
traditional batik.

33:33.226 --> 33:33.825
(Laxie)
Look.

33:34.385 --> 33:35.145
You have to

33:35.345 --> 33:36.825
draw the lines

33:36.906 --> 33:38.385
with beeswax

33:38.746 --> 33:39.785
before dyeing.

33:41.226 --> 33:42.585
But modern industry

33:43.026 --> 33:44.105
uses machines

33:44.305 --> 33:45.506
to replicate

33:45.506 --> 33:47.065
handmade effects

33:47.305 --> 33:48.305
at a lower cost.

33:49.145 --> 33:51.186
Craftsmen who insist
on the manual approach

33:51.345 --> 33:52.506
are dwindling.

33:53.746 --> 33:54.986
Excuse me, Ms. Qiuzi.

33:56.145 --> 33:57.906
Is there no original piece of this?

33:57.946 --> 33:59.065
Why is it a photo?

34:00.506 --> 34:00.906
This is

34:01.105 --> 34:01.946
the work of

34:01.986 --> 34:03.145
a local veteran craftsman.

34:03.466 --> 34:04.706
We're displaying the photos

34:04.906 --> 34:06.305
because we can't get the original.

34:06.506 --> 34:07.426
A local craftsman?

34:07.706 --> 34:08.105
Yeah.

34:09.346 --> 34:11.306
A local artisan created these patterns

34:11.306 --> 34:12.426
peculiar to Southwestern

34:14.065 --> 34:15.265
ethnic minority groups.

34:15.466 --> 34:16.466
This master craftsman

34:16.585 --> 34:18.906
once lived in Miao ethnic villages.

34:19.386 --> 34:19.946
Therefore,

34:20.145 --> 34:21.306
he brought back

34:21.306 --> 34:22.105
their techniques.

34:22.906 --> 34:23.466
Look.

34:23.665 --> 34:24.986
His style leans heavily

34:25.026 --> 34:26.105
towards traditional

34:26.145 --> 34:27.065
folk patterns.

34:27.786 --> 34:29.506
Our designer at Yan Studio

34:29.585 --> 34:31.585
happens to be from the Yi ethnic group.

34:32.585 --> 34:33.466
If she saw

34:33.506 --> 34:34.466
such a design,

34:35.026 --> 34:35.946
she'd be thrilled.

34:37.105 --> 34:37.705
Ms. Qiuzi,

34:38.386 --> 34:39.906
could you share his contact?

34:40.306 --> 34:41.506
I want to inquire about

34:41.826 --> 34:42.866
licensing this pattern.

34:43.625 --> 34:45.185
I'm afraid that won't be possible.

34:46.225 --> 34:47.946
He stopped making these three years ago.

34:50.065 --> 34:50.545
Why?

34:51.826 --> 34:53.625
Creative block, perhaps?

34:54.745 --> 34:55.466
He's reluctant

34:55.466 --> 34:56.946
to discuss batik.

34:57.545 --> 34:58.946
He even took back

34:59.065 --> 35:00.585
his displayed works.

35:03.625 --> 35:05.105
That's so bad.

35:06.386 --> 35:07.185
What a shame.

35:09.545 --> 35:10.866
You can try.

35:11.986 --> 35:12.506
But

35:12.705 --> 35:13.705
I don't know

35:14.185 --> 35:15.145
if he'll agree.

35:15.290 --> 35:18.545
(Laxie)

35:18.545 --> 35:19.665
I actually know

35:20.946 --> 35:21.826
Master Chu.

35:24.625 --> 35:25.346
You know him?

35:26.426 --> 35:27.145
Years ago,

35:27.145 --> 35:28.826
Jinda ran welfare programs

35:28.946 --> 35:29.866
in Gubei Town

35:29.866 --> 35:31.065
where we delivered supplies.

35:32.105 --> 35:33.866
I delivered supplies to Mr. Chu.

35:34.625 --> 35:36.545
And I saw him again here last year.

35:37.346 --> 35:38.665
But he's quite reclusive

35:38.745 --> 35:39.665
and doesn't like

35:40.185 --> 35:41.306
social interactions.

35:41.585 --> 35:42.946
I didn't know that

35:43.145 --> 35:44.386
he was an expert in batik.

35:45.346 --> 35:46.426
If you want to meet him,

35:46.986 --> 35:47.946
I'll go with you.

36:01.050 --> 36:03.504
(Cash only,
10 yuan per pile, self-service)

36:07.026 --> 36:07.705
Who is it?

36:12.625 --> 36:13.786
Haoming, why are you here?

36:14.225 --> 36:15.265
I brought something.

36:16.265 --> 36:17.065
You're so kind.

36:17.866 --> 36:18.506
And this is?

36:19.786 --> 36:20.346
My friend.

36:21.585 --> 36:22.545
Please, come in.

36:23.105 --> 36:23.786
Thank you.

36:25.065 --> 36:25.866
Take a seat.

36:26.026 --> 36:27.225
Let me make some tea.

36:42.225 --> 36:42.906
Haoming.

36:43.346 --> 36:44.866
It's been so long.

36:45.426 --> 36:45.906
Yeah.

36:46.545 --> 36:47.585
I've been busy with work.

36:48.466 --> 36:49.506
The gardening techniques

36:50.545 --> 36:52.665
you taught me last time

36:52.986 --> 36:53.585
were amazing.

36:54.185 --> 36:55.426
Look at all my plants.

36:55.665 --> 36:56.386
I noticed.

36:56.906 --> 36:57.826
Next time, I'll bring

36:57.866 --> 36:59.065
some gardening books

36:59.145 --> 37:00.185
that you can use.

37:00.225 --> 37:01.105
Thank you.

37:04.466 --> 37:05.665
Your friend here...?

37:06.625 --> 37:07.585
Nice to meet you.

37:07.625 --> 37:08.466
I'm Xu Yan.

37:09.306 --> 37:10.545
I run a clothing company

37:10.625 --> 37:11.946
in Jingzhou.

37:13.506 --> 37:14.745
I'll cut to the chase.

37:15.705 --> 37:16.866
We're currently integrating

37:16.946 --> 37:18.585
intangible cultural heritage

37:18.665 --> 37:19.866
into our designs.

37:25.946 --> 37:28.026
We saw your batik works

37:28.225 --> 37:29.585
at the dyeing workshop.

37:30.065 --> 37:31.265
They're stunning.

37:31.866 --> 37:33.466
It would be meaningful

37:33.665 --> 37:35.346
to feature your patterns

37:35.705 --> 37:37.105
in our latest

37:37.786 --> 37:39.506
batik-inspired collection.

37:42.545 --> 37:43.986
We hope you'll authorize us

37:45.225 --> 37:46.705
to use the patterns.

37:49.105 --> 37:50.026
Haven't you heard?

37:50.466 --> 37:51.506
I quit ages ago.

37:56.145 --> 37:56.705
Then

37:57.225 --> 37:59.745
could we use your previous works?

38:00.946 --> 38:01.585
Haoming.

38:03.786 --> 38:05.145
I invited you in

38:05.185 --> 38:06.065
out of respect.

38:06.466 --> 38:07.026
Sir.

38:07.386 --> 38:08.386
Please don't be mad.

38:08.545 --> 38:10.386
She was genuinely moved by your work.

38:10.705 --> 38:11.346
I'm sorry.

38:11.506 --> 38:11.946
Stop trying

38:12.265 --> 38:12.946
to fool me.

38:13.386 --> 38:14.506
My mediocre creations

38:14.545 --> 38:15.705
couldn't move anyone.

38:16.185 --> 38:17.105
Let me be honest.

38:17.625 --> 38:18.545
I'd rather let

38:18.866 --> 38:20.585
my batik works rot at home.

38:20.906 --> 38:21.426
I don't care.

38:21.786 --> 38:22.826
I enjoy it.

38:24.506 --> 38:25.946
I think you should leave.

38:26.665 --> 38:27.105
Sir.

38:27.386 --> 38:28.240
Give us a minute.

38:28.240 --> 38:30.160
- Master Chu, sorry.
- Let her explain.

38:36.665 --> 38:37.745
I've been thinking.

38:38.225 --> 38:38.866
Actually,

38:39.306 --> 38:40.665
I was indeed rude.

38:41.386 --> 38:43.145
I jumped straight into business matters.

38:43.466 --> 38:44.585
That's why he was

38:44.866 --> 38:45.906
so irritated

38:45.906 --> 38:46.625
and harsh.

38:46.826 --> 38:47.625
It's not your fault.

38:48.265 --> 38:49.265
It only shows

38:49.466 --> 38:50.265
that he's still

38:50.745 --> 38:52.065
against batik art.

38:52.545 --> 38:53.105
But

38:53.585 --> 38:54.745
he hasn't let go yet.

38:54.906 --> 38:56.065
I was about to tell you.

38:56.346 --> 38:57.585
I saw blue-dyed fabrics

38:57.786 --> 38:58.986
covered by plastic sheets

38:59.225 --> 39:00.625
in his backyard earlier.

39:01.625 --> 39:03.065
Did you notice the Assam indigo

39:03.265 --> 39:04.426
soaking in vats?

39:05.145 --> 39:06.786
That's the botanical dye for blue.

39:07.585 --> 39:09.105
Why'd someone who hates coriander

39:09.386 --> 39:10.986
keep it in their fridge?

39:14.426 --> 39:15.225
Then why...?

39:16.386 --> 39:17.225
Let's see someone

39:17.625 --> 39:18.466
who knows everything.

39:19.866 --> 39:20.426
Who?

39:20.665 --> 39:21.426
Chu

39:21.625 --> 39:23.105
got divorced three years ago.

39:23.466 --> 39:24.528
He's just making excuses.

39:24.986 --> 39:26.466
He blamed it on the divorce

39:26.786 --> 39:27.585
that he lost

39:27.906 --> 39:29.026
his inspiration.

39:29.506 --> 39:30.545
Lost his inspiration?

39:30.906 --> 39:32.026
How did that happen?

39:32.466 --> 39:33.105
He lost

39:33.105 --> 39:34.466
his dyeing partner.

39:35.105 --> 39:36.545
Chu knows batik techniques

39:37.026 --> 39:38.065
but indigo dyeing

39:38.225 --> 39:40.866
is his wife's specialty.

39:41.306 --> 39:42.946
They were the perfect partners.

39:43.225 --> 39:43.826
Truth be told,

39:44.265 --> 39:45.545
her indigo blues

39:45.786 --> 39:46.545
were mesmerizing.

39:47.225 --> 39:48.906
If they're such a perfect match,

39:48.946 --> 39:49.906
why did they divorce?

39:50.386 --> 39:51.346
His wife

39:51.506 --> 39:53.105
was a Miao girl from Guizhou.

39:53.145 --> 39:54.466
She met Chu when she was 19

39:54.466 --> 39:56.745
while he studied dyeing in her village.

39:56.946 --> 39:58.545
It was love at first sight.

39:58.745 --> 39:59.545
She insisted on

40:00.145 --> 40:00.752
marrying him

40:00.826 --> 40:02.705
and left her homeland

40:03.026 --> 40:03.625
with him.

40:04.506 --> 40:05.745
That sounds

40:05.866 --> 40:06.625
quite romantic.

40:07.745 --> 40:08.585
Romantic beginning.

40:08.946 --> 40:09.826
Ugly ending.

40:10.306 --> 40:11.585
She thought Chu

40:11.866 --> 40:12.786
was outdated.

40:13.185 --> 40:13.866
Chu felt that

40:14.026 --> 40:15.625
she despised his lack of ambition

40:16.306 --> 40:17.386
and earnings.

40:17.745 --> 40:19.065
Living with mutual resentment

40:19.105 --> 40:19.946
doomed

40:20.105 --> 40:21.545
their marriage.

40:21.906 --> 40:22.866
So they got divorced

40:23.225 --> 40:24.306
and cut all ties.

40:24.986 --> 40:25.906
The painter

40:26.145 --> 40:26.946
and the dyer

40:27.466 --> 40:28.705
ended up like a pen

40:28.745 --> 40:29.585
without ink.

40:30.065 --> 40:30.585
Nonsense.

40:30.906 --> 40:31.745
Those are excuses.

40:31.745 --> 40:32.506
Guys are the same.

40:33.506 --> 40:34.386
No offense.

40:36.506 --> 40:38.065
From what I just heard,

40:38.625 --> 40:40.466
there are no fundamental issues

40:41.426 --> 40:42.906
or severe conflicts between them.

40:43.265 --> 40:43.745
Why

40:45.265 --> 40:46.185
don't they reconcile?

40:49.506 --> 40:50.906
Master Chu and his wife

40:50.906 --> 40:52.466
met due to batik art.

40:54.265 --> 40:55.506
Now Master Chu refuses

40:56.065 --> 40:57.225
to produce any artworks.

40:57.866 --> 40:59.105
He's clearly holding grudges

40:59.545 --> 41:00.705
against his ex-wife.

41:05.225 --> 41:06.026
The real pity

41:08.026 --> 41:09.105
isn't the batik craft,

41:09.866 --> 41:10.946
but their relationship.

41:35.786 --> 41:36.545
Caught a cold?

41:37.625 --> 41:39.026
Maybe. It's chilly.

41:42.145 --> 41:42.986
You're burning up.

41:43.346 --> 41:44.065
You have a fever.

41:45.745 --> 41:47.265
It's fine. I'll rest a bit.

41:47.265 --> 41:48.185
This won't do.

41:48.506 --> 41:49.866
Ask Dr. Yu to pick you up.

41:50.946 --> 41:52.265
He's got major surgery today.

41:52.306 --> 41:53.265
It's just a fever.

41:53.585 --> 41:54.506
Don't distract him.

41:57.105 --> 41:58.585
(Yan Studio)
And I can't walk away

41:59.145 --> 41:59.986
from so much work.

42:01.105 --> 42:02.866
Is it about the loan?

42:04.705 --> 42:05.506
I've been talking

42:05.545 --> 42:07.265
to our suppliers all day,

42:07.745 --> 42:09.265
asking for payment extensions.

42:09.545 --> 42:10.466
Nobody would budge.

42:10.946 --> 42:11.745
I'm going crazy.

42:12.185 --> 42:13.786
What about Mr. Liang's investment?

42:15.225 --> 42:16.026
Yuanhang wants us

42:16.026 --> 42:17.466
to expand offline markets.

42:17.866 --> 42:19.306
That funding is earmarked

42:19.506 --> 42:20.625
and allocated.

42:21.026 --> 42:22.265
I've approached several banks

42:22.745 --> 42:23.705
about loans.

42:24.145 --> 42:25.906
With Yan Studio's current scale,

42:26.705 --> 42:28.105
they can approve two million.

42:29.866 --> 42:30.346
Really?

42:30.625 --> 42:31.346
Chill.

42:32.346 --> 42:32.986
Let's see.

42:33.225 --> 42:33.986
We'll work on it

42:34.026 --> 42:35.026
if there's progress.

42:35.466 --> 42:35.986
Alright.

42:38.466 --> 42:39.906
Let me find a thermometer.

42:43.545 --> 42:44.466
39.8 Degrees Celsius.

42:45.466 --> 42:45.826
Lin.

42:46.105 --> 42:46.466
Let's go

42:46.705 --> 42:47.346
to the hospital.

42:47.545 --> 42:47.946
Hurry.

42:48.105 --> 42:49.065
Don't be dramatic.

43:01.105 --> 43:01.506
Lin.

43:02.026 --> 43:02.826
You need to rest.

43:03.306 --> 43:04.625
I'll boil some water for you.

43:04.826 --> 43:05.585
No need, Lin Tao.

43:06.145 --> 43:07.105
I got this.

43:08.265 --> 43:08.866
Could you

43:09.105 --> 43:10.426
go back to the office

43:10.786 --> 43:11.866
to fetch my phone?

43:11.986 --> 43:13.506
Sure, I'll get it for you.

43:13.826 --> 43:14.745
Take care of yourself.

43:15.322 --> 43:15.826
(Certificate)

43:15.826 --> 43:16.265
Thanks.

43:16.306 --> 43:16.826
No problem.

43:18.682 --> 43:22.096
(Yu Yiming)

43:31.225 --> 43:31.786
Yu Yiming.

43:32.145 --> 43:32.665
Lin Tao?

43:33.906 --> 43:34.986
How come it's you?

43:35.585 --> 43:36.208
Where's Lin?

43:36.368 --> 43:37.265
She's having a fever.

43:37.265 --> 43:38.826
We rushed to the hospital

43:39.306 --> 43:40.185
and I came to pick up

43:40.225 --> 43:41.065
her phone she left

43:41.306 --> 43:42.145
at the office.

43:42.426 --> 43:43.105
Where is she now?

43:43.625 --> 43:44.265
At home.

43:44.786 --> 43:45.466
Head there now.

43:45.906 --> 43:46.545
I'm on my way.

43:47.065 --> 43:47.986
Meet at her place.

43:48.545 --> 43:48.946
Okay.

43:49.105 --> 43:49.786
Be right there.

43:55.665 --> 43:56.105
Lin Tao.

43:56.145 --> 43:56.545
Finally.

43:56.665 --> 43:57.185
Where's Lin?

43:57.665 --> 43:58.506
In her room.

43:58.786 --> 43:59.545
Fever's gone down.

44:01.826 --> 44:02.426
It almost

44:02.826 --> 44:03.866
turned into pneumonia.

44:04.545 --> 44:05.105
Her phone.

44:05.386 --> 44:05.906
Thank you.

44:06.466 --> 44:07.026
No problem.

44:09.225 --> 44:09.745
Well,

44:10.545 --> 44:11.506
don't get me wrong

44:12.745 --> 44:13.625
for taking her back.

44:14.426 --> 44:15.625
We're just fellow townsfolk

44:15.625 --> 44:16.625
and coworkers now.

44:19.265 --> 44:19.745
I won't.

44:21.346 --> 44:21.986
Good then.

44:22.346 --> 44:23.786
I left the medicine

44:24.026 --> 44:24.826
on the table.

44:25.346 --> 44:25.986
I wrote down

44:26.386 --> 44:27.145
the dosage.

44:27.585 --> 44:29.065
You're the doctor. You know better.

44:29.705 --> 44:30.506
Go ahead.

44:30.826 --> 44:31.426
I'm off.

44:32.625 --> 44:33.026
Lin Tao.

44:36.986 --> 44:38.105
Thank you so much.

44:39.585 --> 44:40.265
Take care of her.

44:41.026 --> 44:41.506
Go on.

44:52.145 --> 44:52.826
Master Chu.

44:54.705 --> 44:55.906
Why are you here again?

44:57.306 --> 44:58.225
You're not welcome.

44:58.225 --> 44:58.786
Master Chu.

44:59.065 --> 45:00.026
Don't call me master.

45:00.026 --> 45:00.625
Please.

45:00.986 --> 45:01.826
I just don't get it.

45:02.386 --> 45:03.786
There are plenty of dyers around.

45:04.665 --> 45:05.466
Find someone else.

45:06.625 --> 45:07.426
We...

45:08.065 --> 45:08.906
Sir.

45:11.105 --> 45:12.306
Good artworks

45:12.506 --> 45:13.585
call for sharing.

45:14.346 --> 45:16.545
If you hide them from people,

45:16.906 --> 45:17.826
you'll never know

45:17.866 --> 45:19.185
how others view your work.

45:19.665 --> 45:20.105
Okay.

45:20.185 --> 45:21.065
You say you lack

45:21.346 --> 45:22.145
inspiration.

45:22.665 --> 45:23.265
Then why not

45:23.265 --> 45:24.426
try to communicate

45:24.426 --> 45:25.545
with others?

45:26.225 --> 45:27.145
That's how you infuse

45:27.426 --> 45:28.946
your creations with vitality.

45:31.786 --> 45:32.386
Oh boy.

45:33.185 --> 45:35.026
I don't need your lectures.

45:35.946 --> 45:38.026
I wouldn't dare lecture you, sir.

45:38.306 --> 45:39.265
I just want to

45:39.306 --> 45:40.545
help you break through

45:40.625 --> 45:41.506
and see if you can

45:41.506 --> 45:42.946
keep producing artworks.

45:44.585 --> 45:45.265
Listen.

45:45.545 --> 45:46.466
New things

45:46.665 --> 45:48.065
aren't scary at all.

45:48.906 --> 45:51.265
Modern technology assists humans

45:52.105 --> 45:53.145
in overcoming confusion

45:53.145 --> 45:53.986
about creation.

45:54.426 --> 45:55.426
If you can't weave

45:55.466 --> 45:56.145
or draw

45:56.506 --> 45:57.185
certain patterns,

45:57.506 --> 45:58.585
AI could help with that.

45:59.386 --> 46:01.346
Technology serves us

46:01.665 --> 46:02.665
and helps us...

46:02.786 --> 46:04.306
What nonsense!

46:05.145 --> 46:05.986
I don't believe

46:06.026 --> 46:06.745
in AI stuff.

46:07.466 --> 46:09.705
If computers can replace humans,

46:10.386 --> 46:11.225
why do you still

46:11.506 --> 46:12.265
come to me?

46:12.665 --> 46:14.506
You think creation is that easy?

46:15.145 --> 46:17.545
Computers can't replace human minds.

46:18.625 --> 46:20.866
You're not resisting new things.

46:21.225 --> 46:22.745
You don't want to change, do you?

46:24.906 --> 46:26.065
You're right.

46:26.826 --> 46:28.225
I won't change.

46:30.346 --> 46:31.665
I'm successful

46:31.946 --> 46:34.386
because I stay true to myself.

46:34.585 --> 46:36.545
I never cater to others' opinions.

46:37.065 --> 46:38.745
So you're not against batik.

46:38.826 --> 46:40.426
You're avoiding your true self.

46:42.225 --> 46:43.386
If you've stopped creating

46:44.506 --> 46:45.346
batik works,

46:45.866 --> 46:47.786
what's the indigo in the backyard for?

46:50.466 --> 46:51.545
You and your ex-wife

46:52.346 --> 46:53.026
were spouses

46:53.145 --> 46:54.426
and the best partners.

46:56.065 --> 46:58.105
Without her color-mixing,

47:00.306 --> 47:01.225
you'll never find

47:01.225 --> 47:02.386
that perfect shade of blue.

47:03.625 --> 47:04.225
Is that it?

47:09.625 --> 47:10.585
Enough.

47:11.466 --> 47:12.346
Don't be so smart.

47:12.386 --> 47:13.625
I'll tell you the truth.

47:13.826 --> 47:15.866
I'm out of inspiration.

47:17.185 --> 47:17.705
Master Chu.

47:17.786 --> 47:18.386
- Master Chu.
- I...

47:35.065 --> 47:36.625
So it's not like only his wife

47:37.346 --> 47:39.265
could create that blue hue.

47:39.906 --> 47:41.105
In fact, that blue hue

47:42.426 --> 47:43.426
embodies his wife.

47:46.705 --> 47:47.705
He knows it very well,

47:48.866 --> 47:50.585
but he refuses to admit it.

47:51.386 --> 47:52.705
Failing to dye blue

47:53.145 --> 47:54.466
and lacking inspiration

47:55.585 --> 47:57.265
are not the real issues.

47:58.265 --> 47:59.386
Deep down,

48:00.185 --> 48:01.306
he hasn't let go of her.

48:07.625 --> 48:08.426
You can't

48:09.545 --> 48:11.185
wake someone pretending to sleep.

48:12.426 --> 48:14.545
I actually understand him a bit now.

48:16.506 --> 48:17.705
You think he's right?

48:19.466 --> 48:20.346
He reminds me

48:21.426 --> 48:23.026
of who I used to be.

48:28.065 --> 48:30.986
Extremely self-centered

48:32.466 --> 48:33.506
and controlling.

48:34.625 --> 48:35.585
Do you remember

48:35.946 --> 48:37.145
how to cultivate agave?

48:39.265 --> 48:40.026
We can't

48:40.026 --> 48:41.466
let it grow on its own.

48:42.625 --> 48:43.585
We have to

48:43.625 --> 48:45.665
intervene all the time.

48:47.946 --> 48:48.946
Master Chu is the same.

48:50.185 --> 48:51.386
He doesn't want to change.

48:52.065 --> 48:53.105
Once changes occur,

48:53.346 --> 48:54.426
he becomes uneasy.

48:55.386 --> 48:56.745
He forces people around him

48:56.946 --> 48:58.386
to follow his ways.

48:59.426 --> 49:01.026
So, he didn't get divorced

49:02.065 --> 49:03.185
because his wife

49:03.625 --> 49:05.705
looked down on his failures.

49:06.426 --> 49:07.786
He was running away

49:08.986 --> 49:10.225
from his wife's attempts

49:10.826 --> 49:12.065
to make him break out

49:12.986 --> 49:14.866
of his shell and adapt to the changes.

49:17.065 --> 49:17.906
So?

49:19.466 --> 49:21.225
Have you cured your need for control?

49:23.585 --> 49:24.426
Still working on it.

49:38.346 --> 49:38.745
Look.

49:39.906 --> 49:40.866
See this bridge?

49:41.946 --> 49:43.466
We've crossed it many times.

49:44.386 --> 49:45.346
I just never realized

49:45.946 --> 49:47.466
it looks so beautiful from afar.

49:48.506 --> 49:50.426
When we rush towards destinations,

49:50.946 --> 49:52.386
we miss the scenery.

49:54.705 --> 49:56.026
It's like

49:56.026 --> 49:59.386
how we interact with nature.

49:59.786 --> 50:00.386
When you stand

50:00.426 --> 50:01.585
on the bridge,

50:01.866 --> 50:03.265
it feels like self-reflection.

50:03.946 --> 50:04.665
But when others

50:04.665 --> 50:06.386
see you standing there,

50:07.145 --> 50:08.105
it's a different view.

50:09.105 --> 50:10.026
That's why

50:10.386 --> 50:12.225
self-awareness

50:12.506 --> 50:13.466
isn't easily achieved.

50:17.906 --> 50:18.745
When was your

50:18.786 --> 50:19.306
first visit?

50:22.105 --> 50:22.705
I first

50:22.745 --> 50:23.906
visited here

50:23.946 --> 50:25.986
when Haochen was four.

50:26.466 --> 50:28.426
I came back from my studies abroad
and brought him

50:28.545 --> 50:29.145
here.

50:30.225 --> 50:31.625
He must have loved it.

50:32.545 --> 50:33.145
Yeah.

50:34.346 --> 50:35.185
He was curious

50:35.225 --> 50:36.826
about me, the brother

50:36.946 --> 50:38.306
who had just returned.

50:39.026 --> 50:40.306
One day, he said he didn't

50:40.426 --> 50:41.665
want to go to kindergarten.

50:42.826 --> 50:44.306
So I told Mom that

50:44.386 --> 50:45.545
I'd take him to school.

50:46.225 --> 50:48.265
But I drove him out for an adventure.

50:48.346 --> 50:49.185
And we came here.

50:50.105 --> 50:50.826
So, Haochen's

50:52.826 --> 50:53.946
mischievous nature

50:54.826 --> 50:55.906
is half your fault.

50:56.866 --> 50:57.506
Fair point.

50:58.145 --> 50:59.786
I missed much of his growing up.

51:00.585 --> 51:01.786
That's not entirely true.

51:03.225 --> 51:04.386
You've done well.

51:05.145 --> 51:06.786
A child's attitude and reactions

51:07.065 --> 51:08.065
tell the whole story.

51:08.986 --> 51:10.026
Haochen adores you

51:10.265 --> 51:10.986
and relies on you.

51:11.906 --> 51:12.705
You did well.

51:15.225 --> 51:16.185
The first time

51:16.506 --> 51:17.506
we came here,

51:17.906 --> 51:19.506
we had so much fun.

51:20.426 --> 51:21.466
Everything here

51:21.466 --> 51:22.306
felt new

51:22.786 --> 51:24.026
and exciting to me.

51:24.906 --> 51:25.545
There was this

51:25.545 --> 51:26.826
amazing ice cream shop.

51:27.265 --> 51:29.225
He wolfed down two scoops at once

51:29.705 --> 51:30.826
and made me promise

51:32.026 --> 51:34.026
not to tell Mom.

51:34.946 --> 51:35.745
He gave me

51:35.745 --> 51:36.906
a huge hug

51:37.426 --> 51:38.185
and a kiss.

51:40.946 --> 51:41.826
That was

51:43.585 --> 51:44.986
his first time hugging me.

51:47.026 --> 51:48.065
It was so warm.

51:50.466 --> 51:51.545
That's when I realized

51:52.585 --> 51:53.466
that this town

51:54.306 --> 51:55.265
could give him

51:56.426 --> 51:57.105
childhood joys

51:57.105 --> 51:57.906
that every kid

51:57.946 --> 51:58.786
deserves

51:59.705 --> 52:00.386
and help him

52:00.426 --> 52:01.786
rediscover the nature of a kid.

52:03.306 --> 52:05.306
Later, I made this town

52:05.826 --> 52:07.906
his personal paradise.

52:08.585 --> 52:09.225
I hoped he could

52:09.225 --> 52:10.466
live like regular kids,

52:11.745 --> 52:13.185
being mischievous and joyful.

52:22.986 --> 52:24.466
This place works the same way

52:24.585 --> 52:25.346
for me.

52:25.906 --> 52:26.625
It's simple

52:27.105 --> 52:27.866
and pure.

52:28.986 --> 52:29.906
No matter

52:29.946 --> 52:30.866
what troubles come,

52:32.145 --> 52:33.545
whether I argue with my dad

52:33.826 --> 52:35.265
or face issues at Jinda,

52:35.745 --> 52:36.426
coming here

52:36.745 --> 52:37.665
always calms my mind

52:37.665 --> 52:38.665
like magic.

52:40.545 --> 52:41.585
That's why I've been

52:42.346 --> 52:43.866
renovating buildings and facilities

52:44.466 --> 52:45.426
under Jinda's name

52:45.745 --> 52:47.105
over the years.

52:48.026 --> 52:49.065
It's not for profit.

52:50.346 --> 52:51.786
I just hope to make this place

52:52.265 --> 52:53.145
even better.

52:55.866 --> 52:56.585
Want to try?

53:01.866 --> 53:02.346
Like this?

53:02.625 --> 53:03.105
No.

53:03.386 --> 53:04.026
Like this.

53:05.185 --> 53:05.776
Put strength.

53:07.665 --> 53:08.185
Here we go.

53:09.665 --> 53:10.026
Come on.

53:10.506 --> 53:11.088
Put strength.

53:11.265 --> 53:12.466
Same posture as yours?

53:13.386 --> 53:14.826
One, two, three.

53:14.946 --> 53:15.346
Go!

53:16.826 --> 53:17.705
Natural talent.

53:17.906 --> 53:18.466
One more.

